						<div class="postbody">For the specific instance of byte-swapping 16-bit words (i.e. ABCD becomes BADC), the extremely ancient and open-source program <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dd_(Unix)" class="postlink">dd</a> can do that using <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">conv=swab</tt>.</div>

